hy is interesting.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.044713,0.087436,0.099244,0.10239,0.099851,0.095157,0.092303,0.087023,0.082534,0.079002,0.069461,0.060883],"unified_progress":[0.058221,0.075832,0.086784,0.096299,0.097901,0.097162,0.095308,0.092882,0.088346,0.083979,0.070694,0.056592]},{"section":11,"text":"Usually, muscle weakness might lead to atrophy, but in some cases, like Duchenne muscular dystrophy, the calves can become enlarged.","dimension":6,"group":2,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03564,0.072779,0.085358,0.095657,0.10204,0.10248,0.10318,0.096774,0.088967,0.084832,0.072697,0.059598],"unified_progress":[0.079248,0.068236,0.081783,0.088258,0.094013,0.10105,0.096615,0.095511,0.088306,0.083858,0.068879,0.054239]},{"section":12,"text":"High CPK levels indicate muscle damage.","dimension":2,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03494,0.074588,0.090296,0.097282,0.099482,0.097685,0.10013,0.094837,0.08969,0.083738,0.076087,0.061241],"unified_progress":[0.076927,0.076546,0.084799,0.092013,0.097079,0.095663,0.093871,0.091466,0.085737,0.081259,0.070211,0.054428]},{"section":13,"text":"Duchenne is an X-linked recessive disorder, so more common in boys.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034042,0.070069,0.083047,0.09272,0.098905,0.1016,0.10112,0.096842,0.090004,0.088909,0.076084,0.066651],"unified_progress":[0.074782,0.085375,0.089359,0.090169,0.091568,0.095549,0.091149,0.092164,0.083704,0.079907,0.068636,0.057636]},{"section":14,"text":"The age also fits because Duchenne typically presents around 3-5 years, but maybe this kid is a bit older.","dimension":11,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.042795,0.079113,0.084354,0.088836,0.093393,0.099902,0.09651,0.096133,0.089645,0.087814,0.076894,0.064612],"unified_progress":[0.081895,0.10538,0.095714,0.091177,0.088243,0.090486,0.084335,0.089701,0.079484,0.076133,0.064954,0.052498]},{"section":15,"text":"Other possibiliti